            <form>
               <orth>starrag</orth>
            </form>
            <def>a crow.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="AOHenley_ScolpaigWMacDonaldmisc-idp112518872">
            <form>
               <orth>susaladh</orth>
            </form>
            <def>marking out an area of land to be dug. I would pronounce this as ‘sussadh’.</def>
         </entry>
